In [7]:
calories = pd.read_csv('hourlyCalories_merged.csv')
calories.ActivityHour = pd.to_datetime(calories['ActivityHour'])
intensities = pd.read_csv('hourlyIntensities_merged.csv')
intensities.ActivityHour = pd.to_datetime(intensities['ActivityHour'])
steps = pd.read_csv('hourlySteps_merged.csv')
steps.ActivityHour = pd.to_datetime(steps['ActivityHour'])
merged_hours = pd.merge(calories,intensities,how='outer',left_on=['Id','ActivityHour'],right_on=['Id','ActivityHour'])
merged_hours = pd.merge(merged_hours,steps,how='outer',left_on=['Id','ActivityHour'],right_on=['Id','ActivityHour'])
In [8]:
import calendar

merged_hours['weekday'] = merged_hours.ActivityHour.apply(lambda x: calendar.day_name[x.weekday()])
merged_hours['hour'] = merged_hours.ActivityHour.apply(lambda x: x.hour)
cats = ['Monday', 'Tuesday', 'Wednesday', 'Thursday', 'Friday', 'Saturday', 'Sunday']
merged_hours['weekday']= pd.Categorical(merged_hours['weekday'], categories=cats, ordered=True)

In [13]:
def non_zero_mean(a):
    return a[a>0].mean()
each_Id_report = active.groupby('Id')[num_cols].agg([non_zero_mean, np.count_nonzero])
In [14]:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns
distances=['TotalDistance',
           'LoggedActivitiesDistance', 'VeryActiveDistance',
           'ModeratelyActiveDistance', 'LightActiveDistance',
           'SedentaryActiveDistance']
minutes=['VeryActiveMinutes', 'FairlyActiveMinutes',
         'LightlyActiveMinutes', 'SedentaryMinutes']
steps=['TotalSteps']
calories=['Calories']


fig, axs = plt.subplots(2,3,figsize=(15, 10))
axs = axs.ravel()
for i,col in tqdm(enumerate(distances)):
    ids=each_Id_report.xs("count_nonzero", level=1, axis=1, drop_level=True).reset_index().query('TotalSteps>15')
    df= each_Id_report.xs("non_zero_mean", level=1, axis=1, drop_level=True).reset_index()
    x =df.loc[df.Id.isin(ids.Id),col]
    sns.histplot(x, label=col,  kde=True,ax=axs[i])
    plt.legend()
